Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:01:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Driven to Desperation!\N The Shadow of Temptation"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The morning of the battle is finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally here, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head out to our final battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:02:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, Jounouchi. We're gonna head on up to the balcony so we can cheer you guys on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, Jounouchi. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, the time to settle things has come at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... I'm impressed you showed up, considering all that awaits you is a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keith, I don't know squat about you being the ex-U.S. Champion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll beat the shit outta a creep like you with my cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess you still ain't realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without the card needed to participate in the tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you'll lose before you even {\i0}enter{\i1} the Duel Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention all Duelists participating in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please enter the Duel stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, proud Duelists, to this sacred Dueling battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duelist Kingdom Championship Tournament shall now commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who survives the tournament shall be granted a prize deserving of a champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a prize that big, I can save Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, the winner shall earn the right to challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can you answer one thing, Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the person get if they defeat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who defeats me, the creator of Duel Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shall be recognized as the "Duelist King" and the founder of Industrial Illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the one who defeats me shall be awarded the title of the world's number one Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recognized by everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I presume the Duelists among me would gladly accept both great fortune and fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't {\i1}that{\i0} interestin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely wonder who will win the tournament and challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to defeat you no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And get back everyone's souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first round will now commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou VS Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please proceed to the Duel Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we start, please show me the cards earning you the right to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see much better from up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You better win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku... I must win this Duel so I can move on to battle Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beating strong opponents is a Duelist's greatest thrill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came to this island for the sole purpose of that thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after meeting you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I began to question my way of living, and learned the meaning of friendship from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I dreamed of the moment I could finally fight against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! Your very existence is what got me this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, you're not even {\b0}looking{\b1} at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seems his heart is already set on his fight against Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the one mistake you mustn't make.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't win a Duel when you don't even have your enemy within sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to use those special "Aroma Tactics"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to use those against {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai, I'm sorry, but you're no match against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something you can't see right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you can't see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you have no hope of beating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mai Kujaku's usual strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mai's overused strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think the same strategy she used on {\i1}me{\i0} will beat {\i1}Yugi{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'll play another card this turn as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Set Card, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just play a strong card and dispose of the Harpie Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Harpie Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a big idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Screened Mirror Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Shaver!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Screened Mirror Wall is a Trap Card that halves the Attack Points of a Monster that attacks it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you attack it, this mirror appears to stop your assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after attacking the reflection of itself in the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attacking Monster will have its Attack split in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place an Equipment Card on my Harpie Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyber Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going, Harpie Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch Clash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Knight Gaia has been annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My powerful card Gaia... was destroyed...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I didn't think you would fall for something so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright... Demon's Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has enough Attack Points to beat the powered up Harpie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now come on and attack me, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I face you with this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the extent of my power, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish off the Harpie Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just declared "attack", Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Trap Card will reactivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, the Demon's Attack Points are halved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! A {\i1}Permanent{\i0} Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap still remains on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you noticed a bit too late, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally once activated, a Trap Card will lose its powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the card will disappear from the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there {\i1}are{\i0} some exceptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Out of the hundreds of Trap Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Wall is one of the rarest Traps, a Permanent Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as this card remains on the field, I can activate its effects again and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time you declare "attack"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, that makes all of your Monsters' attacks completely useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Yugi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be playing rashly without thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like him to fall for the same trick twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... what's {\i1}wrong{\i0} with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the Duelist I've admired for so long was only at this level...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can clearly see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment you stepped into the Duel Ring, you've been crushed by an invisible pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An invisible pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Duelists face each other in battle, they can feel their fighting aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not feeling that aura from you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say you can't feel any fight in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only thinking about fighting Pegasus, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're looking right past {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're more of an arrogant {\i1}boy{\i0} than a strong {\i1}man{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you already beat me before the Duel even began.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're distracted by the thought of Pegasus watching us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you think of our battle as a mere {\i1}nuisance{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pressure... from Pegasus...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy... That lady is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the way your mind is now, you hold no {\i1}chance{\i0} of ever defeating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! Say what you want {\i1}after{\i0} you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just continue the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a {\i1}weak{\i0} man to try and intimidate his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're just bluffing to hide your {\i1}own{\i0} weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on the mark, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you fell into my trap so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn Mai...! She's always trying to provoke her opponents...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Don't let Mai toy with you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san... Why are you acting this way towards Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be Mai-san's trying to help Yugi not lose sight of his Duelist ability...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Win or lose, the cruelties of the world still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in the end, all you can rely on is {\i1}yourself{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai-san won't forgive Yugi unless he fights her with everything he has... his full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm {\i1}seriously{\i0} angry, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you've finally woken up, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe now we can have a {\b0}real{\b1} Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! This time it's the {\i1}real{\i0} battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As A Duelist, you must face me with 100% of your power and your pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or there's no meaning to me defeating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will he attack Harpie with Demon this turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's Yugi's Set Card that bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's very likely to be a Trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn, I attack using this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie's Feather Duster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Set Card was Hexagram Curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had you attacked, you would have fallen for my Trap Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read through it nicely, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a very cautious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a bit {\i1}too{\i0} cautious at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as she has Silver Screened Mirror Wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't attack her, no matter how many Attack Points my Monsters have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My attacks are sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon to Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also place a Monster in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stand no chance of winning if you're trapped like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use the Equipment Card Rose Whip to increase Harpie Lady's Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you plan to infinitely power up your Harpie while hiding behind Silver Screened Mirror Wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start by attacking that Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whip Punish!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not yet, Yugi...! My Harpie Combo is {\b0}far{\b1} from complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Will Yugi be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Mai's gonna create her Harpie Lady Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Keep trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as Mai continues to use that Trap Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no point in trying to defend yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take you out nice and slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, my Harpie Combo is 70% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's not complete yet, this is more than enough to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Harpie's strongest servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie's Pet Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady's cute, well-trained pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie's Pet Dragon gains 300 Attack Points for every Harpie Lady on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, eliminate that Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Fire Giga!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Demon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... there's something you've lost sight of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And until you find that answer, you stand no chance of beating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I fought against Jounouchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he asked me a riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, now it's time for me to direct that riddle at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something you can see, but can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I wonder if you can find the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you can see, but can't see...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, ain't that the {\i1}same{\i0} question I asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, do you even know the answer yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, I've come up with my own answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll answer in place of Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that answer is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fiery, {\i1}fiery{\i0} spirit of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! That's incorrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My answer's not such a cliché!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cliché?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what the hell {\i1}is{\i0} the correct answer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sides, me and Yugi thought of it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi... You were the one who taught me that answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you should know what that answer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do you think a card amateur like you made it this far in the Duelist Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me that and you've got your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the way Yugi is now, he'll never find that answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now's not the time to be confused by Mai's words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll win this Duel with my own strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Black Magician card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harpie's Pet Dragon has 2300 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In terms of Attack Power, Black Magician is stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she still has the Silver Screened Mirror Wall Trap on her field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll play a Trap {\b0}against{\b1} a Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Black Magician in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then, Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you attack my Black Magician, Holy Barrier Mirror Force will destroy your Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this card, my Harpie Combo will be 80% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, there's no point in setting a trap for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My next card is the Equipment Card, Shadow of Temptation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow of Temptation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By looking at your magician, you'll know what it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician took a fighting stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Shadow of Temptation has the power to lure enemies into battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Harpie's battle pheromones stimulates an enemy's battle instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She switched him into Attack Mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So that means Yugi's Defense has been sealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go on and attack the Harpie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll play this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie's Feather Duster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Trap Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Harpie's Pet Dragon will attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Fire Giga!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Harpie Combo is perfect, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is bad, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(141,140)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you can see, but can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san's words help Yugi take back what he's lost so he can begin his counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Mai-san's impenetrable strategies, he's backed into a big pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's found some kind of trump card to turn the tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! "The Legendary Strongest Soldier: Chaos Soldier Descends"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:21:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:22:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
